# ── Rust ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/target
**/target
Cargo.lock.orig

# ── Node / TS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
.vite/
*.tsbuildinfo
.pnpm-store/
# Render-gate harness output (screenshots + diff summary) — never committed;
# the one endorsed gate artifact is copied to docs/verification/ by hand.
verify-out/

# ── GeoBase data — NEVER commit geospatial data or secure vaults ────────
# Lesson from the prototype: 46 GB of data was co-located with code.
# Code + specs + small fixtures only. Real data lives outside VCS.
/data/**
*.gpkg
*.tif
*.tiff
*.laz
*.las
*.nc
*.shp
*.shx
*.dbf
*.prj
*.cpg
*.geojson
# Secure vaults / TSDF T2–T3 artifacts must never be tracked
*.sgpkg
*.vault
place.toml

# ── Env / secrets / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
*.key
*.pem
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Local working notes — the repo is the Heart; our process stays local ─
# Session handoffs, AI-assisted planning, and scratch notes never ship.
docs/handoffs/
docs/_local/
*.local.md
NOTES.local.md

# ── Re-includes (must come last so negation wins) ───────────────────────
!/data/README.md
!/data/.gitkeep
!/data/fixtures/
!/data/fixtures/**
.codex-runs/
